	   <tr><td colspan=2>has anyone played a Vah Shir bard yet if so are they decent? how are wood elf bards? i was also thinking about starting a Half Elf but i really dont know any thoughts or suggestions would be appreciated<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
